        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "What does it mean to be called to worship? All serious activity requires preparation. The\nand blessings that precede 17, Bar'chu are warm-ups for the individual. Now communal\nbegins. The leader asks, “Are you ready to pray?\" And we respond, \"Yes! Let us pray!\"\nprayers\nprayer\nadapted from Richard Levy",
          "language": "en"
        }
